title: Dope Wars 2.1/2.2 Original
description:
This is the Original Dopewars game by Beermat Software. Serial Key is included. I have included both 2.1 and 2.2 versions of the game.

2.2 version includes several improvements like

- New score encryption
- 120 Day game length
- Weapons and text editor - change the weapons and fight text to your own choice
- Extra end of game statistics showing breakdown of score
- Fixed the zero cash loan bug
- Play changes - can not take more than one loan per day, bank interest rate reduced to 3%

Both versions come with several additional advertising software. You can skip that in 2.1 version but not sure about the 2.2 version.

Enjoy!
